{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Shopify AI Task: Insert Merged 'Engage the Visionary' Form
    
    1. Placement: * This section must be the final "Call to Action" block on the Press Page. Set a 150px top and bottom padding to give it a "Sovereign" breathing space.
    
    2. Layout (50/50 Split):
    
        Image Side (Left): Use the Black & White photo (with the audience hands raised at the World Relief Gala). Crop it to be a powerful vertical portrait. Apply a soft fade effect at the bottom of the image to blend into the footer.
    
        Form Side (Right): Create a clean, white-background inquiry form.
    
    3. The Header (Quiet Authority):
    
        Eyebrow (Soft Grey): THE CALL TO CONVENE
    
        Title (Sovereign Serif): Engage the Visionary
    
        Sub-Header (The Whisper): "Our mission is a documented miracle. We open the gates at 5:55 PM daily to review inquiries for the restoration of hope." (This includes the "Sovereign Anchor" details). Give me control access to adjust photo box size freeform. and give me control access to chagne text size, font, boldness, color and to give me access to adjust padding on top and bottom of segment and in between each information category. , give me options to add 5 more questions in the form fields. so create 5 more boxes. only show the form field box if there is a question. , Task: Update the 'Engage the Visionary' Media Inquiry Form
    
    1. Structural Update: Modify the existing contact form on the Press Page.
    
    2. Map the Following Fields:
    
        Field 1: Full Name & Title
    
        Field 2: Organization / Media Outlet
    
        Field 3: Professional Contact Email (Required)
    
        Field 4: Direct Liaison Number (Optional)
    
        Field 5: Engagement Type (Dropdown Menu)
    
            Options: Broadcast Feature, Editorial / Cover Story, Keynote Dialogue, Documentary / Film Collaboration.
    
        Field 6: The Vision (Text Area)
    
            Helper Text: "Describe the narrative you wish for Nancy Vuu to deliver."
    
        Field 7: Proposed Timeline (Date Picker)
    
    3. Update the Styling:
    
        Subheader: Set the text above the form to: "Admission to the Atelier is by private inquiry. We review each request with the utmost consideration for legacy and global alignment."
    
        Button Text: 'INITIATE THE DIALOGUE' (All Caps, Playfair Display Bold).
    
    4. Success Message (Post-Submit):
    
        "Thank you for initiating the dialogue. We hold each inquiry in high regard and look forward to the possibility of a shared narrative. Our Atelier will acknowledge your request within 48 hours."
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
